messages.content: Hello! I'm your AI voice assistant. I'm here to help you with any questions or conversations you'd like to have. How can I assist you today?
Hi there! I'm doing well, thanks for asking. How about you?
I have a lot of general knowledge on various topics like history, science, tech, and more, all the way up to October twenty-twenty-three. What are you curious about?
That’s totally fine! If you think of anything later, just let me know.
